==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Vega
<hw>Ve"ga</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.]</ety> <def>An
open tract of ground; a plain, esp. one which is moist and fertile, as
those used for tobacco fields.</def> <mark>[Sp. Amer. & Phil.
Islands]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

